Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.64,0:01:47.58,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淑女與武士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.22,0:01:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜蘭克·居爾布
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.73,0:01:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯特利亞國王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.29,0:01:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是提高聲望的最佳舞臺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗殺國王麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 只是個把觀光當國家產業的小國
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且身為初出茅廬的暗殺者既能在業界中提高聲望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那報酬也絕對少不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.68,0:02:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委託人是他的親人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.21,0:02:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不用你管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我保證絕不會演變成外交問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.石川..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯特利亞大公國國家展覽會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:26.67,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Principaute De astria Exposition Nationale
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可謂..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.73,0:02:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界的寶貝齊聚一堂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冰冰冰淇淋給給給你！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬥鬥鬥鬥牛犬在在那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.49,0:02:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布布布丁凍糕呀呀呀呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:03:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家聚在一塊朋友多多..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 發現武士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.34,0:03:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬爾科
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸喜歡的一張畫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 武士！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武~武武武..武士之友！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.54,0:03:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種歌詞 媽媽寫的曲子裏沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛想出來的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武武武士之友..呀呀呀吼~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.07,0:03:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以妨礙到叔叔們的工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪利亞老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就回國了哦
