Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.46,0:04:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冰冰冰淇淋給給給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬥鬥鬥鬥牛犬在在那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武武武武士之友呀呀呀吼！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬爾科
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發前進
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您想必也很累了吧 杜蘭克大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 外交可沒那麼輕鬆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是能和孫子們一起共渡週末時光真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女教師也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是指瑪利亞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是約聘到秋天的臨時家教 但是做的確實不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 如果女兒能有她一半的能耐的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜蘭克大人 這件事就不要再提了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐已經嫁到舒梅特家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 父王不可能聽得進去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇太子已經死了 因為交通事故..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 失去哥哥的父王終日陷於惆悵之中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來的王女是妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.15,0:05:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我就是..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥留下的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.11,0:05:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬爾科才是繼承人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還只是個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼掌管得了這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是這個時候才是我們出場的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做全憑父王的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.81,0:05:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不打算照看那三個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 葛瑞絲妳看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:05:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:05:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是巴黎的淑女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像媽媽一樣..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛瑞絲 媽媽已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是..可是露易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 不是說好不哭的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冰冰冰淇淋給給給..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我拿冰淇淋來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬爾科 危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武..武武士之友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子 馬爾科很喜歡武士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前在盧浮宮博物館也對浮世繪特別感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幾個小孩嘴裏唱的武士之友到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是她們姐弟三人喜歡的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士之友是.. 我想就是同伴的意思吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友是同伴麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而妳就是他們的母親？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我只是一個普通的家教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幾個孩子的雙親三年前因事故去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫瑪利亞 請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.24,0:07:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下是..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用茶 武士之友！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫馬爾科吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂男子漢不要因區區冰淇淋而輕易落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.48,0:07:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是男子漢的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 男子漢的約定！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到這裡居然有武士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼之前都沒有發現呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.12,0:08:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 兔子先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿月之夜月兔現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是日本的景物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.93,0:08:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下名為石川五衛門
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一名流浪藝人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石川先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看呀看呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:08:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬爾科
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:07.76,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}繼承人的血緣之爭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:07.76,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}箭頭指向舒梅特男爵？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面把舒梅特講成繼承人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼承人是馬爾科大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜蘭克大人 這文章看了有害無益
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在馬爾科成人之前 我會保護這個國家！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有害無益麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實斬了個無謂之物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然被女色所迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切捨御免！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:51.45,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}切捨御免：格殺勿論。是日本武士之特權，受到賤民無禮對待之時，可當場斬殺不守責罰。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:09:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們來我這探險嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:09:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,..剛才有個武士好帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少..此時留他們一刻安詳才是武士之義
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:09.50,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(615,610)}甜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 武士先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 在日本還有像你一樣的武士..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非也 現在的日本根本沒有武士的容身之處
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才開始了旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是在下是..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡都找不到自己的容身之處
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是妳有那些孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:10:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朋友在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我只是一個微不足道的臨時約聘的家教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼晚安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士之友先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一般的雜耍藝人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發前進
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜蘭克國王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.66,0:11:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.石川..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.34,0:12:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停..停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊..緊急聯絡！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.04,0:12:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,列車失控了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.63,0:12:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 無法取得聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜蘭克大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按這個速度下去 列車很快就會脫軌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.39,0:12:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底出了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 你們..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人搞破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員被人殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您應該很清楚是誰幹的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:12:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個玩雜耍的竟如此出言不遜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我回座位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有刺客！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把刀扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.91,0:13:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管 開槍吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士之友！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世間萬物..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有此斬鐵之劍切不斷的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.30,0:13:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好..好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是何方聖神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下的名字是石川五衛門
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.43,0:14:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下是前來取你的性命的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然冒充成雜耍藝人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞破壞的也是你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個事態..並非在下所願
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來聽聽你要說什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托蘭克大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.89,0:14:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪利亞老師 讓孩子們和乘客趕緊去避難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到列車的最後一節
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切的錯要歸咎於在下的稚嫩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石川先生..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬爾科說要去救爸爸的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 妳們倆先逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是暗殺麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因不相信在下的手段才出此下策..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一開始就是雙重的計劃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人就是這樣的小人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然在下也成了他們的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒必要取你性命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個事態 請讓我來負責吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪利亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.60,0:15:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.90,0:15:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬爾科去了貨物車廂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.74,0:15:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的武士..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬爾科！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪利亞老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.14,0:15:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想把加速減到最小
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貨物車廂的重量實在太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是國寶都放在那個車廂裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國寶和小孩子的性命哪個更重要？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧 馬爾科
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師..好帥..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬爾科！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 我們趕緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.03,0:15:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 瑪利亞老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士之友會救我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會哭的 因為和他約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好樣的 馬爾科
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪利亞老師 請抓緊時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我要把孩子們固定好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家請拿一些皮帶給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的..夠不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪利亞老師 用我的皮帶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又斬了無謂之物..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 全世界的寶貝統統都..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冰冰冰淇淋給給給你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬥鬥鬥鬥牛犬在在那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武武武武士之友吼吼吼！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家聚在一塊朋友多多~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,託你的福 我們得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟你道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無須道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下乃生活在暗處之人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就此告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請跟孩子們..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟馬爾科道個別
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天會和朋友相逢..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.49,0:17:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛瑞絲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬爾科
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 我們回城堡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父王！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也都沒事真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.石川
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男爵您應該心裏明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請跟我們走一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒梅特男爵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士之友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬爾科 要成為了不起的國王哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你什麼時候開始在這等的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是同類麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 武士之友先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是刺客..或是盜賊麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國寶也都付之一炬了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好白費功夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那些孩子得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,託了妳的福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太看得起我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是那塊料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是何許人也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報上名來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何許人也？只是一個女人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊 是大公國代代傳下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:20:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48}傳說中奧古斯特·羅丹偷偷送給情人卡米耶·克洛岱爾的..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“哀求的國王”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就是以這個為目標麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 全部都是在演戲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.99,0:20:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣？很受打擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.82,0:20:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這樣就對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..所以妳也同為天涯淪落人呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何況誰都沒有真正的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是和在下的話..可以做真正的..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和在下的話 可以做真正的什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是峰不二子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.41,0:20:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有緣再會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.79,0:20:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出色的武士之友先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.32,0:20:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做真正的女朋友..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再會啦 五衛門
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:21:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,峰..不二子醬..麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是何許人也！？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又斬了無謂之物..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.94,0:21:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待續
